description: Phoenix Phreeze Shaved Ice is locally owned and operated by Arizona natives and was started as a way to recapture the excitement we all felt as kids when we heard the ice cream truck, walked to the candy store, or elbowed up to a snack bar. There was nothing like seeing that amazing assortment of sweet treats and knowing that we could choose whatever one we wanted.With Phoenix Phreeze you can have that feeling again, whether you find it out and about, or bring it to your very own party. So what are you waiting for? Get yourself a sweet treat today!
name: Phoenix Phreeze
